  <abstract>Image of four women posting with Greek War Relief Association collection boxes looking at a poster that reads &quot;Lest It Be Too Late! Help Greece Now.&quot; Photographic print has been painted over to obscrue the identities of three women.  Verso reads: &quot;In a final appeal to Toronto citizens for money to buy food for the gallant Greeks, over 2,000 taggers for the Greek War Relief Fund will be on Toronto streets to-morrow.  Here Miss Helen Corolis and Mrs. Mildred LePordevin, with their tag boxes are looking at the tage day poster with its poignant message, &quot;Lest it be too late - help Greece Now.&quot;</abstract>
